  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT2.11">
<l>cūṭu matiyañ caṭaimē luṭaiyār cuḻalvār tirunaṭṭa</l>
<l>māṭu marava maraiyi lārtta vaṭika ḷaruḷālē</l>
<l>kāṭu malinta kaṉalvā yeyiṟṟuk kāraik kāṟpēytaṉ</l>
<l>pāṭaṟ pattum pāṭi yāṭap pāva nācamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Grace to the feet of him who possesses on [his] matted hair the adorning moon,</l>
<l>who has tied snakes to [his] middle when dancing the revolving upright sacred dance,</l>
<l>[there is] the destruction of sins when one sings [and] dances all ten in the song</l>
<l>of the demoness from Kāraikkāl with teeth [in her] fire mouth, spoken on/rejoicing in the cremation ground.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
